long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
With WorkMind, you can search Google and ChatGPT simultaneously, allowing you to find answers to your questions faster than ever before. 

WorkMind also includes a collection of prompts that you can use to start conversations with ChatGPT. These prompts are designed to spark your imagination and help you explore new ideas and topics.

Stay tuned to WorkMind.ai to completely revolutionize the way you work. Sign up for early access to explore how we're changing work productivity.
long.de,es,fr,he,hu,ja,ko,pt_PT,ro,ru,uk,zh_C:
It’s perfect for anyone who wants to quickly and easily access the knowledge and expertise of ChatGPT without having to navigate to a separate website or application. 

Whether you're looking for information on a specific topic, need help with a task, or just want to engage in a conversation with an intelligent AI, the ChatGPT Chrome extension is the perfect solution.
long.en_US:
With Enhanced ChatGPT, you can search Google and ChatGPT simultaneously, allowing you to find answers to your questions faster than ever before. 

And if you love using ChatGPT, you'll be pleased to know that Enhanced ChatGPT gives you access to ChatGPT everywhere you go on the web.

But that's not all! Enhanced ChatGPT also includes a collection of prompts that you can use to start conversations with ChatGPT. These prompts are designed to spark your imagination and help you explore new ideas and topics.

Overall, Enhanced ChatGPT is the ultimate tool for anyone who wants to save time, increase productivity, and access the latest in artificial intelligence technology. 

Disclaimer: This extension is not an official OpenAI product, but rather an amazing tool built by amazing people.
